# Custom Shopify Slick Slider

A modern custom Shopify slider section built using Liquid, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery, and Slick Slider.

## Features

- Dynamic image upload from Shopify customizer
- Slick slider integration
- Autoplay functionality
- Navigation arrows
- Dots indicator
- Text overlay content
- CTA buttons
- Responsive design
- Modern UI layout

---

# Technologies Used

- Shopify Liquid
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- jQuery
- Slick Slider

---

# Installation

## 1. Create Section File

Create a new file inside:

```bash
sections/custom-slider.liquid
```

---

## 2. Paste the Code

Paste the complete slider code inside the file.

---

## 3. Add Section in Theme Customizer

Go to:

```bash
Online Store → Customize → Add Section
```

Select:

```bash
Custom Slider
```

---

